sequenceDiagram
    participant Investor
    participant Portal as DALP Portal
    participant Policy as Compliance Engine
    participant Registry as Identity Registry
    participant Chain as Blockchain
    participant Custody

    Investor->>Portal: Request transfer / redemption
    Portal->>Registry: Resolve identity & wallet
    Registry-->>Portal: Verified profile
    Portal->>Policy: Evaluate jurisdiction, whitelist, limits
    Policy->>Policy: Check holding rules & eligibility
    Policy-->>Portal: Approved / rejected
    alt Approved
        Portal->>Chain: Execute token transfer / burn
        Chain-->>Custody: Emit settlement event
        Custody-->>Investor: Release metal or cash leg
    else Rejected
        Portal-->>Investor: Explain failed rule
    end
